items.title: Winning numbers drawn in Monday’s Powerball

items.title: A Florida county leads the way with a high-tech 911 system that improves emergency response
items.description: Collier County, Florida, uses one of the most advanced 911 systems in the U.S., allowing callers to send texts and videos

items.title: Murder trial begins for Colorado dentist accused of poisoning wife's protein shakes
items.description: A Colorado dentist accused of killing his wife of 23 years by poisoning her protein shakes begins trial with opening arguments this week

items.title: Florida man who killed 2 people outside a bar is scheduled to be executed
items.description: A man convicted of fatally shooting a man and woman outside a Florida bar as part of an attempted revenge killing is scheduled to be executed

items.title: Mike Waltz to face grilling over Signal chat at Senate hearing for UN role
items.description: Mike Waltz will face questioning from lawmakers for the first time since he was ousted as national security adviser
